### Environment variables
###
### Copy to .env.local (do not commit real values).
###
### Canonical production origin. All canonical URLs, OG URLs, sitemap
### entries and JSON-LD IDs are built from this. Fallback in code:
### https://swingpathpro.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://swingpathpro.com

### Google Search Console verification token. Leave empty until you have
### set up GSC. Once you get the meta content string from Google's "HTML
### tag" method, paste it here and redeploy - no code changes needed.
GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION=

### Resend API key, used by src/app/api/contact/route.ts to send the
### contact form. Get one free at resend.com, paste it here and redeploy -
### the contact form will not send email without this set.
RESEND_API_KEY=
